  </head>

  <body>
    <!--==========================
        Header Area Start
    ============================-->

    <%- include("../partials/mainNavbar") %>

    <!--==========================
        Header Area End
    ============================-->

    <!--==========================
        Bradcam Area Start
    ============================-->

    <div class="bradcam_area breadcam_bg overlay">
      <h3>CSR</h3>
      <svg
        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
        viewBox="0 0 1440 315"
        style="display: block"
      >
        <path
          fill="#ffffff"
          fill-opacity="1"
          d="M0,192L80,170.7C160,149,320,107,480,122.7C640,139,800,213,960,224C1120,
        235,1280,181,1360,154.7L1440,128L1440,320L1360,320C1280,320,1120,320,960,320C800,320,640,320,480,320C320,320,160,320,80,320L0,320Z"
        ></path>
      </svg>
    </div>

    <!--==========================
        Bradcam Area End
    ============================-->

    <!--==========================
        CSR Area Start
    ============================-->

    <section class="section-padding">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xl-12 col-lg-12 col-md-12">
            <p data-aos="flip-up">
              As a start-up, it’s our responsibility to be socially responsible.
              Hence our objectives are derived from the six core CSR
              characteristics to become an example for our all our stakeholders
              and to give back to the society by spreading the knowledge learned
              to even the most remote parts of the world.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6">
            <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
              <div class="csr">
                <div class="icon-box">
                  <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right"></i>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="title">Voluntary Work:</h4>
                  <p class="description">
                    We target to join hands with NGOs and firms that share our
                    vision to come together and stand against discrimination and
                    aim to educate everyone with the same level of persistence,
                    quality and passion.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
              <div class="csr">
                <div class="icon-box">
                  <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right"></i>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="title">Managing Externalities:</h4>
                  <p class="description">
                    We work to provide a platform to all the influencers who
                    intent to spread social awareness and stand against the
                    profit making education systems by providing the same level
                    of quality of learning to our clients.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
              <div class="csr">
                <div class="icon-box">
                  <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right"></i>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="title">Multiple Stakeholder Orientation:</h4>
                  <p class="description">
                    Our aim is to spread equality and prioritise our
                    stakeholder’s interests and their development prior to our
                    own financial growth.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-xl-6 col-lg-6 col-md-6">
            <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
              <div class="csr">
                <div class="icon-box">
                  <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right"></i>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="title">Social and Economic Alignment:</h4>
                  <p class="description">
                    Our ambition is to support our audience with education,
                    career, environment, health & wellbeing and economic
                    development by tapping their urge of learning and giving
                    them the best we can!
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
              <div class="csr">
                <div class="icon-box">
                  <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right"></i>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="title">Practices and Values:</h4>
                  <p class="description">
                    We prioritise our values and practices with the aim to help
                    the community and also provide our own interns and employees
                    the best working atmosphere to develop themselves.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="container" data-aos="fade-up">
              <div class="csr">
                <div class="icon-box">
                  <div class="icon">
                    <i class="fa fa-arrow-circle-o-right"></i>
                  </div>
                  <h4 class="title">Beyond Philanthropy:</h4>
                  <p class="description">
                    Our coming project is focused on Women empowerment to help
                    female influencers, leaders, trainers, entrepreneurs and
                    students to spread their wings and fight for their
                    educational, career and human rights.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!--==========================
        CSR Area End
    ============================-->

    <!--==========================
        Footer Area Start
    ============================-->

    <%- include("../partials/mainFooter") %>

    <!--==========================
        Footer Area End
    ============================-->

    <!--==========================
        JS Area 
    ============================-->
    <%- include("../partials/mainScripts") %>
  </body>
</html>
